   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "2.160",
   "children": [],
   "end": "4.880",
   "id": "f000003",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "C\u1edb sao m\u00e0 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 vi\u1ebft ra kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u th\u1ebf?"
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "4.880",
   "children": [],
   "end": "10.320",
   "id": "f000004",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "M\u1ed9t t\u1ed1i kia c\u1eadu h\u1ecfi ch\u00e0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i th\u1ea5y anh ta c\u00f3 v\u1ebb b\u1ef1c b\u1ed9i v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i s\u00e1ch ."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "10.320",
   "children": [],
   "end": "10.320",
   "id": "f000005",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    ""
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "10.320",
   "children": [],
   "end": "14.400",
   "id": "f000006",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "\u0110\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 nh\u1eefng ai th\u1eadt nghi\u00eam ch\u1ec9nh nghi\u1ec1n ng\u1eabm m\u1edbi hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4i, anh ta \u0111\u00e1p ."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "14.400",
   "children": [],
   "end": "14.400",
   "id": "f000007",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    ""
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "14.400",
   "children": [],
   "end": "19.720",
   "id": "f000008",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "C\u1eadu th\u1eed ngh\u0129 m\u00e0 xem, n\u1ebfu ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebfn ch\u1ec9 th\u00e0nh v\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00ec v\u00e0ng c\u00f2n g\u00ec l\u00e0 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb ."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "19.720",
   "children": [],
   "end": "19.720",
   "id": "f000009",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    ""
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "19.720",
   "children": [],
   "end": "24.760",
   "id": "f000010",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Ch\u1ec9 nh\u1eefng ai ki\u00ean t\u00e2m tr\u00ec ch\u00ed, ch\u1ec9 nh\u1eefng ai nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u nhi\u1ec1u m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0110\u1ea1i c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "24.760",
   "children": [],
   "end": "26.040",
   "id": "f000011",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "26.040",
   "children": [],
   "end": "33.080",
   "id": "f000012",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadn gi\u1eefa sa m\u1ea1c n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 luy\u1ec7n kim \u0111an ch\u00ednh c\u1ed1ng gi\u00fap t\u00f4i gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 c\u00e1i ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef b\u00ed m\u1eadt kia ."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "33.080",
   "children": [],
   "end": "33.520",
   "id": "f000013",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    ""
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "33.520",
   "children": [],
   "end": "35.560",
   "id": "f000014",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Nh\u1eefng s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ebft h\u1ed3i n\u00e0o?"
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "35.560",
   "children": [],
   "end": "37.640",
   "id": "f000015",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "C\u1eadu h\u1ecfi T\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ebf k\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "37.640",
   "children": [],
   "end": "41.080",
   "id": "f000016",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "H\u1ed3i \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0m g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u00e1ch in, c\u1eadu kh\u0103ng kh\u0103ng c\u00e3i."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "41.080",
   "children": [],
   "end": "44.680",
   "id": "f000017",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Th\u00e0nh ra kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u1ea5t k\u00ec ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt luy\u1ec7n kim \u0111an."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "44.680",
   "children": [],
   "end": "49.040",
   "id": "f000018",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "V\u1eady th\u00ec vi\u1ec7c g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ee9 ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef k\u00ec qu\u1eb7c kia v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3 h\u1ecda?."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "49.040",
   "children": [],
   "end": "55.320",
   "id": "f000019",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Anh kia kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu m\u00e0 n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e3 quan s\u00e1t \u0111o\u00e0n l\u1eef h\u00e0nh m\u1ea5y ng\u00e0y nay song ch\u1eb3ng ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n g\u00ec m\u1edbi."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "55.320",
   "children": [],
   "end": "59.400",
   "id": "f000020",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "\u0110i\u1ec1u duy nh\u1ea5t anh ta c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e1nh nhau c\u1ee9 d\u1ed3n d\u1eadp th\u00eam ."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "59.400",
   "children": [],
   "end": "59.400",
   "id": "f000021",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    ""
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "59.400",
   "children": [],
   "end": "63.920",
   "id": "f000022",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "M\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y n\u1ecd c\u1eadu \u0111\u01b0a tr\u1ea3 s\u00e1ch cho anh ta Sao, c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ee9?"
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "63.920",
   "children": [],
   "end": "74.360",
   "id": "f000023",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Anh ta h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c, v\u00ec c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u00ean \u0111i n\u1ed7i lo s\u1ee3 s\u1eafp x\u1ea3y ra \u0111\u00e1nh nhau T\u00f4i h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1eb1ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u00f3 t\u00e2m linh v\u00e0 ai hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e2m linh \u1ea5y s\u1ebd hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 v\u1eadt."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "74.360",
   "children": [],
   "end": "82.800",
   "id": "f000024",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "T\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00e0 luy\u1ec7n kim \u0111an \u0111\u00e3 s\u1ed1ng theo con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00ecnh v\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n ra t\u00e2m linh v\u0169 tr\u1ee5, \u0110\u00e1 t\u1ea1o v\u00e0ng v\u00e0 Thu\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng sinh ."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "82.800",
   "children": [],
   "end": "82.840",
   "id": "f000025",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    ""
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "82.840",
   "children": [],
   "end": "88.360",
   "id": "f000026",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ed1t y\u1ebfu t\u00f4i h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i ghi v\u1eeba tr\u00ean m\u1ed9t phi\u1ebfn ng\u1ecdc l\u1ee5c b\u1ea3o ."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "88.360",
   "children": [],
   "end": "88.400",
   "id": "f000027",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    ""
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "88.400",
   "children": [],
   "end": "89.720",
   "id": "f000028",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Anh ch\u00e0ng kia th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng qu\u00e1."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "89.720",
   "children": [],
   "end": "97.520",
   "id": "f000029",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Bao nhi\u00eau n\u0103m nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u1eefng k\u00ed hi\u1ec7u th\u1ea7n di\u1ec7u, nh\u1eefng t\u1eeb b\u00ed hi\u1ec3m, nh\u1eefng d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee5 th\u00ed nghi\u1ec7m  ch\u1eb3ng g\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u00ec n\u01a1i g\u00e3 n\u00e0y c\u1ea3 ."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "97.520",
   "children": [],
   "end": "97.520",
   "id": "f000030",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    ""
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "97.520",
   "children": [],
   "end": "102.480",
   "id": "f000031",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "T\u00e2m h\u1ed3n g\u00e3 qu\u00e1 ch\u1ea5t ph\u00e1c n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, anh ta ng\u1eabm ngh\u0129 ."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "102.480",
   "children": [],
   "end": "102.480",
   "id": "f000032",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    ""
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "102.480",
   "children": [],
   "end": "105.440",
   "id": "f000033",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "R\u1ed3i anh ta \u0111\u00f3n l\u1ea5y s\u00e1ch, nh\u00e9t v\u00e0o t\u00fai cho l\u1ea1c \u0111\u00e0 th\u1ed3 ."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "105.440",
   "children": [],
   "end": "105.440",
   "id": "f000034",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    ""
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "105.440",
   "children": [],
   "end": "108.680",
   "id": "f000035",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Th\u00f4i c\u1eadu h\u00e3y quay v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi \u0111o\u00e0n l\u1eef h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u0111i v\u1eady."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "108.680",
   "children": [],
   "end": "111.640",
   "id": "f000036",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "T\u00f4i c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec t\u1eeb n\u00f3 c\u1ea3."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "111.640",
   "children": [],
   "end": "116.680",
   "id": "f000037",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "C\u1eadu t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng s\u1ef1 y\u00ean \u1eafng c\u1ee7a sa m\u1ea1c, quan s\u00e1t b\u1ee5i c\u00e1t tung l\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00e2n l\u0169 v\u1eadt ."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "116.680",
   "children": [],
   "end": "116.680",
   "id": "f000038",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    ""
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "116.680",
   "children": [],
   "end": "120.040",
   "id": "f000039",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e0o c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1ea5y, c\u1eadu t\u1ef1 nh\u1ee7."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "120.040",
   "children": [],
   "end": "124.480",
   "id": "f000040",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "C\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a anh ta kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng c\u00e1ch anh ta."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "124.480",
   "children": [],
   "end": "128.800",
   "id": "f000041",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Song c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang \u0111i t\u00ecm con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ed1ng cho m\u00ecnh, n\u00ean m\u00ecnh coi tr\u1ecdng anh ta ."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "128.800",
   "children": [],
   "end": "128.800",
   "id": "f000042",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    ""
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "128.800",
   "children": [],
   "end": "131.920",
   "id": "f000043",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Trong th\u1eddi gian n\u00e0y \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111i c\u1ea3 ng\u00e0y l\u1eabn \u0111\u00eam."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "131.920",
   "children": [],
   "end": "140.680",
   "id": "f000044",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Beduin \u0103n m\u1eb7c k\u00edn t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0a tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi, v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi phu l\u1ea1c \u0111\u00e0 quen c\u1eadu cho bi\u1ebft c\u00e1c b\u1ed9t l\u1ea1c \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1nh nhau r\u1ed3i."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "140.680",
   "children": [],
   "end": "143.920",
   "id": "f000045",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "May m\u1eafn l\u1eafm \u0111o\u00e0n m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 an to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ed1c \u0111\u1ea3o."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "143.920",
   "children": [],
   "end": "146.600",
   "id": "f000046",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "L\u0169 v\u1eadt ki\u1ec7t s\u1ee9c c\u00f2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00e0ng l\u1eb7ng l\u1ebd h\u01a1n."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "146.600",
   "children": [],
   "end": "159.440",
   "id": "f000047",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "\u0110\u00eam khuya thanh v\u1eafng l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 nh\u1ea5t v\u00ec ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ebfng k\u00eau c\u1ee7a l\u1ea1c \u0111\u00e0tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y v\u1ed1n l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng  c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ho\u1ea3ng s\u1ee3, b\u1edfi \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u t\u1eadp k\u00edch Ng\u01b0\u1eddi phu n\u1ecd c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 ch\u1eb3ng b\u1eadn t\u00e2m g\u00ec l\u1eafm tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 \u0111e do\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn tranh ."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "159.440",
   "children": [],
   "end": "159.440",
   "id": "f000048",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    ""
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "159.440",
   "children": [],
   "end": "167.320",
   "id": "f000049",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "T\u00f4i v\u1eabn s\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi gi\u1edd, \u00f4ng ta n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u1eadu trong l\u00fac th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c m\u1ed9t \u0111\u0129a ch\u00e0 l\u00e0 v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00eam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed1t l\u1eeda v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng tr\u0103ng."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "167.320",
   "children": [],
   "end": "170.400",
   "id": "f000050",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 khi \u0103n t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m g\u00ec kh\u00e1c h\u01a1n l\u00e0 \u0103n."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "170.400",
   "children": [],
   "end": "173.000",
   "id": "f000051",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Khi ch\u1ea1y t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m g\u00ec kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i ch\u1ea1y."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "173.000",
   "children": [],
   "end": "176.760",
   "id": "f000052",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "R\u1ed3i n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh nhau th\u00ec c\u00e1i ng\u00e0y t\u00f4i ch\u1ebft c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u01b0 m\u1ecdi ng\u00e0y kh\u00e1c."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "176.760",
   "children": [],
   "end": "179.200",
   "id": "f000053",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng s\u1ed1ng trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 hay t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "179.200",
   "children": [],
   "end": "182.920",
   "id": "f000054",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "182.920",
   "children": [],
   "end": "186.720",
   "id": "f000055",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "N\u1ebfu ta l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng \u1edf trong hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00ec ta l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "186.720",
   "children": [],
   "end": "194.200",
   "id": "f000056",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf ta s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng sa m\u1ea1c n\u00e0y v\u1eabn \u0111ang s\u1ed1ng, r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea7u tr\u1eddi v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7y sao v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u0111\u00e1nh nhau v\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a con ng\u01b0\u1eddi."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "194.200",
   "children": [],
   "end": "200.640",
   "id": "f000057",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn, m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 l\u1edbn v\u00ec \u0111\u1eddi bao gi\u1edd c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng kh\u1eafc ta hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang s\u1ed1ng ."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "200.640",
   "children": [],
   "end": "200.640",
   "id": "f000058",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    ""
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "200.640",
   "children": [],
   "end": "204.800",
   "id": "f000059",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Hai \u0111\u00eam sau, khi h\u1ecd d\u1ecdn ch\u1ed7 ng\u1ee7 th\u00ec c\u1eadu nh\u00ecn l\u00ean ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecd."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "204.800",
   "children": [],
   "end": "214.280",
   "id": "f000060",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "C\u1eadu ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean th\u1ea5y ch\u00e2n tr\u1eddi c\u00f3 v\u1ebb th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00ec tr\u00ean b\u1ea7u tr\u1eddi c\u00f3 t\u1edbi h\u00e0ng tr\u0103m v\u00ec sao Ph\u00eda \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u1ed1c \u0111\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ea5y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi phu n\u00f3i Th\u1ebf sao m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng \u0111i ngay l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3?."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "214.280",
   "children": [],
   "end": "215.880",
   "id": "f000061",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "V\u00ec m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ee7 ."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "215.880",
   "children": [],
   "end": "215.880",
   "id": "f000062",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    ""
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "215.880",
   "children": [],
   "end": "219.320",
   "id": "f000063",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "C\u1eadu m\u1edf m\u1eaft khi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi l\u00f3 d\u1ea1ng \u1edf ch\u00e2n tr\u1eddi."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "219.320",
   "children": [],
   "end": "227.120",
   "id": "f000064",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "\u0110\u00eam tr\u01b0\u1edbc n\u01a1i \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n l\u1ea5p l\u00e1nh \u00e1nh sao, gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng c\u00e2y ch\u00e0 l\u00e0 d\u00e0i ng\u00fat m\u1eaft Ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ebfn n\u01a1i r\u1ed3i, ch\u00e0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh n\u00f3i v\u00e0 th\u1ea5y nh\u1eb9 c\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "227.120",
   "children": [],
   "end": "227.120",
   "id": "f000065",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    ""
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "227.120",
   "children": [],
   "end": "229.480",
   "id": "f000066",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Anh ta c\u0169ng m\u1edbi v\u1eeba th\u1ee9c gi\u1ea5c."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "229.480",
   "children": [],
   "end": "230.880",
   "id": "f000067",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "C\u1eadu kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "230.880",
   "children": [],
   "end": "236.800",
   "id": "f000068",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "C\u1eadu \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 n\u00edn l\u1eb7ng c\u1ee7a sa m\u1ea1c v\u00e0 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ng\u1eafm h\u00e0ng ch\u00e0 l\u00e0 n\u01a1i ch\u00e2n tr\u1eddi kia."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "236.800",
   "children": [],
   "end": "243.200",
   "id": "f000069",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "C\u1eadu c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i \u0111i xa n\u1eefa m\u1edbi t\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Kim T\u1ef1 Th\u00e1p v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng h\u00f4m nay s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 k\u1ec9 ni\u1ec7m."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "243.200",
   "children": [],
   "end": "248.440",
   "id": "f000070",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Nh\u01b0ng l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e2y n\u00f3 l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi phu l\u1ea1c \u0111\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "248.440",
   "children": [],
   "end": "252.960",
   "id": "f000071",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "C\u1eadu th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c n\u00f3, nh\u1edb l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 cho t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "252.960",
   "children": [],
   "end": "261.600",
   "id": "f000072",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "M\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y kia c\u1ea3 ngh\u00ecn c\u00e2y ch\u00e0 l\u00e0 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 k\u1ec9 ni\u1ec7m, nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, v\u1edbi c\u1eadu, ch\u00fang l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng m\u00e1t, l\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0   n\u01a1i tr\u00e1nh chi\u1ebfn tranh."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "261.600",
   "children": [],
   "end": "267.680",
   "id": "f000073",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "H\u00f4m qua, ti\u1ebfng k\u00eau c\u1ee7a con l\u1ea1c \u0111\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y nguy hi\u1ec3m, th\u00ec gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y r\u1eebng ch\u00e0 l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00e1o hi\u1ec7u s\u1ef1 k\u00ec di\u1ec7u ."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "267.680",
   "children": [],
   "end": "267.680",
   "id": "f000074",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    ""
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "267.680",
   "children": [],
   "end": "271.120",
   "id": "f000075",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u00f3i b\u1eb1ng nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef, c\u1eadu ngh\u0129 ."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "271.120",
   "children": [],
   "end": "271.120",
   "id": "f000076",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    ""
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "271.120",
   "children": [],
   "end": "278.160",
   "id": "f000077",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "\u0110o\u00e0n l\u1eef h\u00e0nh t\u1edbi c\u0169ng h\u1ed1i h\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 th\u1eddi gian tr\u00f4i, nh\u00e0 luy\u1ec7n kim \u0111an th\u1ea7m ngh\u0129 khi nh\u00ecn c\u1ea3 tr\u0103m ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0 th\u00fa v\u1eadt t\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ed1c \u0111\u1ea3o ."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "278.160",
   "children": [],
   "end": "278.160",
   "id": "f000078",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    ""
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "278.160",
   "children": [],
   "end": "281.240",
   "id": "f000079",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "D\u00e2n ch\u00fang l\u1edbn ti\u1ebfng h\u00f2 reo ch\u1ea1y v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0111o\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi t\u1edbi."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "281.240",
   "children": [],
   "end": "283.280",
   "id": "f000080",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "B\u1ee5i bay m\u00f9 tr\u1eddi."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "283.280",
   "children": [],
   "end": "287.080",
   "id": "f000081",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "L\u0169 tr\u1ebb reo h\u00f2, nh\u1ea3y nh\u01b0 choi choi khi th\u1ea5y \u0111o\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1ea1."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "287.080",
   "children": [],
   "end": "292.600",
   "id": "f000082",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Nh\u00e0 luy\u1ec7n kim \u0111an th\u1ea5y t\u00f9 tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u1ed1c \u0111\u1ea3o l\u1ea1i ch\u00e0o tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n l\u1eef h\u00e0nh v\u00e0 hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n h\u1ed3i l\u00e2u."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "292.600",
   "children": [],
   "end": "295.440",
   "id": "f000083",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Nh\u01b0ng nh\u00e0 luy\u1ec7n kim \u0111an kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m m\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u1ea5y."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "295.440",
   "children": [],
   "end": "301.000",
   "id": "f000084",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "\u00d4ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng th\u1ea5y nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn r\u1ed3i \u0111i, trong khi \u1ed1c \u0111\u1ea3o v\u00e0 sa m\u1ea1c v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u1ed1c \u0111\u1ea3o v\u00e0 sa m\u1ea1c."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "301.000",
   "children": [],
   "end": "311.040",
   "id": "f000085",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "\u00d4ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5y vua ch\u00faa v\u00e0 k\u1ebb \u0103n xin \u0111i qua bi\u1ec3n c\u00e1t n\u00e0y, c\u00e1i bi\u1ec3n c\u00e1t th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean thay h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed5i d\u1ea1ng v\u00ec gi\u00f3 th\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn m\u00e3i m\u00e3i l\u00e0 c\u00e1i bi\u1ec3n c\u00e1t m\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft t\u1eeb khi c\u00f2n nh\u1ecf."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "311.040",
   "children": [],
   "end": "321.800",
   "id": "f000086",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Tuy v\u1eady, t\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1y l\u00f2ng m\u00ecnh, \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00e0o kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y vui tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u0169 kh\u00e1ch, sau bao ng\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 c\u00e1t v\u00e0ng v\u1edbi tr\u1edd xanh nay \u0111u\u1ee3c th\u1ea5y ch\u00e0 l\u00e0 xanh t\u01b0\u01a1i hi\u1ec7n ra tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft ."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "321.800",
   "children": [],
   "end": "321.800",
   "id": "f000087",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    ""
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "321.800",
   "children": [],
   "end": "327.120",
   "id": "f000088",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Th\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ebf t\u1ea1o ra sa m\u1ea1c ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 cho con ng\u01b0\u1eddi bi\u1ebft qu\u00ed tr\u1ecdng c\u00e2y ch\u00e0 l\u00e0, \u00f4ng ngh\u0129 ."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "327.120",
   "children": [],
   "end": "327.120",
   "id": "f000089",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    ""
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "327.120",
   "children": [],
   "end": "330.640",
   "id": "f000090",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "R\u1ed3i \u00f4ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 h\u01a1n."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "330.640",
   "children": [],
   "end": "334.360",
   "id": "f000091",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "\u00d4ng bi\u1ebft trong \u0111o\u00e0n n\u00e0y c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u00e0 \u00f4ng c\u1ea7n truy\u1ec1n l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n b\u00ed m\u1eadt c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "334.360",
   "children": [],
   "end": "336.360",
   "id": "f000092",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1m b\u00e1o cho \u00f4ng bi\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc ."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "336.360",
   "children": [],
   "end": "336.360",
   "id": "f000093",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    ""
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "336.360",
   "children": [],
   "end": "342.080",
   "id": "f000094",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "\u00d4ng ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1ea5y nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f4i m\u1eaft gi\u00e0 d\u1eb7n c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn ra ngay m\u1ed9t khi \u00f4ng nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y t\u1eadn m\u1eb7t."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "342.080",
   "children": [],
   "end": "345.520",
   "id": "f000095",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "\u00d4ng mong r\u1eb1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e0y c\u0169ng s\u1ebd ham h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng ."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "345.520",
   "children": [],
   "end": "345.520",
   "id": "f000096",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    ""
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "345.520",
   "children": [],
   "end": "353.640",
   "id": "f000097",
   "language": "vi",
   "lines": [
    "Ta kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft t\u1ea1i sao c\u1ee9 ph\u1ea3i m\u1eadt truy\u1ec1n nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng ng\u1eabm ngh\u0129, khi m\u00e0 ch\u00fang ch\u1eb3ng b\u00ed m\u1eadt g\u00ec l\u1eafm, v\u00ec ch\u00ednh Th\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 ph\u01a1i b\u00e0y m\u1ecdi b\u00ed m\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch h\u00e0o ph\u00f3ng cho m\u1ecdi t\u1ea1o v\u1eadt."
   ]
  },
  {
   "begin": "353.640",
   "children": [],
   "end": "354.000",
   "id": "f000098",
